\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.1 Knowledge Base as Authoritative Repository
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The Knowledge Base maintained in the System of Engagement is the authoritative repository for all operational knowledge artifacts governed by this policy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The Assistant IT Director shall ensure that all KB articles are stored in the System of Engagement as the primary repository.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The Assistant IT Director shall maintain at least one secondary accessible medium,
 synchronized no less than monthly,
 in accordance with the operational standard the Assistant IT Director establishes under Section 3.
\end_layout

