,
 including symptoms,
 workaround procedure,
 and Problem record reference.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Upon permanent remediation and Problem closure,
 the Assistant IT Director shall ensure the corresponding entry is marked inactive within the timeframe established in 
